description:
I’m laid back and I laugh often. My sense of humor is probably more twisted
than my sexuality. I find humor in most of life, frequently in the strangest places. I seem to be a bit of a social invalid.I’m just need to fix my gutter mouth and sick/crude/fucked up sense of humour. Who am I….kinky,ugly,old, poor and uninteresting,with a low IQ. Who would I like to be… Barbie and a Nobel prize winner.Oh! and Rich,VERY Rich.!!! But alas I am only me. Why am I here…..sheesh, how would I know? Do you know?
